== Magical spcialties
Affinity for a specific threat: Mark stress to add an ambient threat of that type.


=== Ice elemental magic
[x] Affinity for Ice
[x] Convoque affinity: Ice - Your vessel performs the following actions: Protection (you may cancell an attack die up to Vessel Die Level)
[ ] Ice Attack - 
[ ] Convoque affinity: Ice - Convert any targeted ice into a *trap* threat 
[ ] Ice Rituals

=== Healing magic
[x] Affinity for Water
[x] Convoque affinity: Water - Your vessel performs the following actions: Healing (heal one character by vessel dice pool)
[x] Convoque affinity: Water - Your vessel performs the following actions: Curing (removes one *blight* or *dread* from a character)
[ ] Water attack 
[ ] Water Rituals

=== Fire elemental magic
[x] Affinity for Fire
[x] Convoque affinity: Fire - Your vessel performs the following actions: Blinding light (inflict *Fool* and ends)


=== Necromancy
[x] Affinity for Dread / Blight
[ ] Convoque affinity: Dread - Your vessels becomes undead and attacks using Vessel Dice Pool
[ ] Ceremonial Rituals 

