== Knowledge specialties

=== Socialite
[x] Draw knowledge when you gossip
[x] Reliable test (4) : Influence and persuasion
[ ] Apply Knowledge (Cups / Hearts) :  Influence using Emotions, apply *fool*
[ ] Apply Knowledge (Swords / Spades) : Influence using Threatening, apply *dread*
[ ] Apply Knowledge (Pentacles / Diamonds) : Influence using Bribes, apply *fool*
[ ] Apply Knowledge (Wands / Clubs) : Influence using Leadership, apply *open*

=== Herborist
[x] Draw knowledge when you observe a creature
[X] Passive: When removing a threat, you also remove one stress
[x] Mark Supply: create an healing potion
[x] Reliable test: Foraging (4) (add supply)
[ ] Apply Knowledge (Cups / Hearts) : Create a potion that Soothe (remove *Fire*, *blight*, *dread*, *fool* on character)
[ ] Apply Knowledge (Swords / Spades) : Create a potion that Booms (inflict *Fire*, *blight*, *dread*, *dark*, *fool* on a target) 
[ ] Apply Knowledge (Pentacles / Diamonds) : Create a potion that Fortifies  (Armor 2)
[ ] Apply Knowledge (Wands / Clubs) : Overdrive (applies *fire*, *blight*, *fool*, +1 dice size) for combat

